{"tid":2023160,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇自殺","createTime":"2020-05-18T21:16:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T04:07:14.000Z","uid":318272,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b59197a2cb682b0381e680713571a4a5d83a0418","tid":2023160,"uid":318272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T21:16:33.000Z","msg":"假如一個決心要去死嘅人 <br />\n想問下其他旁觀者係點捻<br />\n唔係話自殺都要考慮其他人嘅睇法<br />\n係純粹好奇 對住一個差唔多要死嘅人 <br />\n有咩說話對佢講"},{"pid":"75524ba574e3f12ae61b3e3c98a1bece747bae45","tid":2023160,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T21:17:29.000Z","msg":"RAP<br />\n來生不做地球人"},{"pid":"11f2533ece23d5cf150b8877015b61672e8e19ce","tid":2023160,"uid":24098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T21:17:53.000Z","msg":"都明嘅"},{"pid":"0c4d6993cadc8f3349d82c79da5650b9dbb5e03e","tid":2023160,"uid":343964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T21:19:03.000Z","msg":"正常，人點都會一死，佢想早死咪早死"},{"pid":"d53eebc147d76aa482bf5889d658290ae3546689","tid":2023160,"uid":354823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T21:21:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a15056d829f22e54644ce13e4333fac0209e0d12","tid":2023160,"uid":24098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d53eebc147d76aa482bf5889d658290ae3546689","tid":2023160,"uid":354823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T21:21:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T21:41:36.000Z","msg":"自殺=以死相搏？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335032fc36594f62eb47c3de3d55ceec4a1b6bd5","tid":2023160,"uid":354823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T21:44:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f72a2cc7e2844da59ddf887c21feb0e26879352","tid":2023160,"uid":204750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T21:45:21.000Z","msg":"體諒到嘅..."},{"pid":"1282cd04e7b23d108a7635b6eaa31a71